  "text": "Existing RBV research indicates that the resources that each firm possesses are critical components of the export channel decision. More specifically, firms with valuable intangible resources enter international markets using direct export channels [CITATION_1] . Direct export channels reduce the risk of resource imitation by competitors [CITATION_2] , while also allowing exporting firms to improve their existing resources by accessing information and knowledge on foreign markets [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
